data.description: Welcome Home! 2 story Home with 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 Bath, 2 Car, located in a quaint neighborhood, close to almost everything, hospital, parks, shopping centers, restaurants, schools and Military Bases. Manicured lawn with automatic sprinkler system, Centralized Air conditioner, Stoned Gas Fireplace in Family Room. Kitchen has lots of cabinets, Huge Pantry for storage, Kitchen island with storage. Upstairs has all the Bedrooms with LOFT.  Upstairs Laundry room, Upstairs Mechanical room. Huge Primary Bedroom with 5 piece Primary Bathroom. Double vanity, Shower,   tub and private toilet room. It has a spacious Floorpan. Neighborhood is great you'll love it. What are you waiting for!!!
